<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ م د:</span> <span class="c2">(هَمَدَتِ)</span> النَّارُ طَفِئَتْ وَذَهَبَتِ الْبَتَّةَ وَبَابُهُ دَخَلَ. وَأَرْضٌ <span class="c2">(هَامِدَةٌ)</span> لَا نَبَاتَ بِهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>